{"word":"ἐπιπείθομαι","slug":"ἐπιπείθομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιπείθομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) (<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a> <el>-πείσομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to be persuaded to</i> a certain end, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to trust to, put faith in</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to comply with, obey</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}